name: MISO Carry Out
description: NEW! Offering carry out is new for Chef Arata. With the high demand of his cooking and limited space within the restaurant, he has decided to give take out orders a try. Whether you simply couldn't wait for a seat at the table, or you prefer to dine at your own location, this steaming hot cup of Misoshiru is bound to hit the spot. *Take out containers are always a balance between convenience and waste. therefore we only use compostable, carbon neutral containers.
